Package: IPVdetection
Title: Minimal IPV Detection Using LLM APIs
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Your", "Name", , "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A minimalist approach to detecting intimate partner violence (IPV) 
    indicators in death investigation narratives using Large Language Model APIs.
    Following Unix philosophy, this package provides simple functions that do 
    one thing well - send text to an LLM and get IPV detection results.
